dc_description_s: Sheet 1: Map shows the Light House Reservation, Statue of Liberty, buildings, and contour lines, sewers, and low water lines. |Sheet 2: The island is shown with buildings, the Statue of Liberty is shown, the Macadam Roadway shown, and wharfs are shown. |Sheet 3: Map shows the Statue of Liberty, a few buildings contour lines, and the sea wall.|Sheet 4: The boundary lines of submerged land is shown, pile wharf and wharf, buildings are drawn (some labeled). Similar to map Hudson-00110 with longer legend and more notes.
